  "title": "LHEA and the Word Spirit",
  "description": "LHEA and the Word Spirit is a charming roguelite adventure about life and death with a unique timeline battle system. May the stars align in your favor!",
  "longDescription": "<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# Innovative timeline battle roguelite in a cozy and charming package!\n<!--text-->\n**CONCEPT**\nMentored by an ancient Word Spirit as old as time, help LHEA seal the In-Between realms by guiding lost souls to their next lives.\n\n~\n\n**GAME LOOP**\nExplore the realms, learn knowledge, optimize your Fate Flute and battle entities to seal the realms and restore balance in the In-Between!\n\nLost souls are scattered throughout the realms. You must free them all without running out of essence or LHEA will transition to her next life on Earth and must restart her attempt to seal the realms at her next visit.\n\n~\n\n**TIMELINE BATTLE SYSTEM**\nEach battle between LHEA and entities works the same way: both sides have a Fate Flute with imbued rings on them acting as a battle timeline.\n\nWhen a battle starts, the timeline moves on its own. Every time a ring is reached, an action is cast.\n\n~\n\n**FATE FLUTE & RINGS**\n\n- Each Fate Flute can have 3 presets of up to 3 rings each.\n- Each ring can have a knowledge word imbued in it for battle casting.\n- Rings can be moved around on the Fate Flute for strategy optimization.\n- Each ring has a level from 3 to 10 - the level determines the maximum amount of letters of the knowledge words you can imbue in them. Explore the realms to gain additional knowledge!\n\n~\n\n**KNOWLEDGE**\n\nThere is a wide array of knowledge to be gained in the In-Between. Most of them are related to a specific realm and can have special outcomes when cast. Consult your knowledge book to see their effects!\n\n~\n\n**KNOWLEDGE TRANSFER**\n\nEvery knowledge points you collect in the In-Between can be converted into useful ugprades and new features to help you become stronger when you start a new run.\n\n~\n\n**REALM MAPS**\n\nEach realm map is procedurally generated with predefined rules when a new In-Between run begins. Special tiles can greatly affect your run and global progression, so exploration can be rewarding!\n\n~\n\n**AND MUCH MORE...!**\n\nIt would ruin the fun a bit if everything was revealed on this page! :) Explore the realms to find out how to optimize your runs and complete your objectives!\n\nMay the stars align in your favor!\n\n~\n\n**About SOUL FUEL GAMES**\n\nCreated in 2023 by solo developer Jo Drolet, Soul Fuel Games aims to create video games filled with LIGHT and unpredictability. LHEA and the Word Spirit is the first game of this new studio.\n\nHead over to their website or give them a follow on social media to stay in touch and receive updates about LHEA or future games!\n\nWe appreciate you\n",
